    <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
            <head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head>
            <p>Dilip Purushottam Chitre was a poet and critic who published in Marathi and English in India's post-independence period, as well as a painter and film-maker.</p>
    </bioghist>
    
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
